title: Hour 1 -In Memory of Bill Russell, Deshaun Watson Decision
itunes:title: Hour 1 -In Memory of Bill Russell, Deshaun Watson Decision
description:
Dan spends some time reflecting on the greatness embodied by legendary Boston Celtic Center Bill Russell, the winningest player in NBA history. And he talks to Jeff Darlington about the fallout from the 6-game suspension handed to Cleveland Browns QB, Deshaun Watson.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
